最新版本:  4.26
更新时间:  2020-05-16 00:54:41 (北京时间)

Thanks for using Calm! This update contains multiple bug fixes and performance improvements.

Be sure to listen to our newest Sleep Stories including “The Natural Wonders of the World,” the second Sleep Story narrated by award-winning actress Eva Green, where you’ll experience the breathtaking beauty of the Northern Lights and the awe-inspiring landscape of the Grand Canyon as you drift off to dreamland. And don’t forget to listen to world-renowned actor Matthew McConaughey’s dreamy story about the mysteries of the universe in “Wonder.”

Now you can practice Mindfulness with your children in a way that they understand and can enjoy too! Calm’s Head of Mindfulness, Tamara Levitt, teamed up with the Thomas and Friends™ engines to help little ones to manage difficult emotions and inspire kindness toward others. And enjoy even more Thomas and Friends™ fun with our newest Sleep Story, “Return to Sodor.”

Be sure to check out our newest music track, “The Mosaic of Transformation,” where composer Kaitlyn Aurelia Smith explores the endless possibilities of electronic instruments.

As always, you can expect an original Daily Calm every day, new Sleep Stories every week, and new meditation programs.
While you’re waiting for this update to download, take a few deep breaths and notice what is happening at this moment.
